Bandwidth Calculator MCP Server
================================
A fully functional MCP server that connects to routers, AIOps solutions,
and network management platforms to calculate overall bandwidth requirements.

Supports:
- SNMP v2c/v3 polling for routers and switches
- REST API connectors for SD-WAN controllers (Cisco Meraki, Viptela, VeloCloud)
- AIOps platform connectors (ThousandEyes, SolarWinds, Dynatrace, PRTG)
- NETCONF/SSH device collection
- Multiple bandwidth calculation models (peak, 95th percentile, average+headroom, forecast)
- Capacity planning, anomaly alerts, and report generation
"""

